description:
This is a 16 minute workout called 'Beginner 15 MINUTE Hill Walk | Treadmill Follow Along! #IBXRunning' from the channel IBX Running.
The workout falls under Cardio/Treadmill and Cardio/Walking.
It's suitable for Beginner fitness levels.
You'll need Treadmill for this workout.
The workout has a The Meditative Grind and The Endorphin Wave vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: Let's grind up 7 Hill intervals. We are staying at the same speed the whole time but the incline will be testing you! Coach Veronica will talk you through this workout. Let's get at it!

15:00 minutes of Hill Walk Intervals

All speeds and inclines are suggestions. Please stay safe and within your comfort zone!

Join our community of runners: http://www.ibxrunning.com
Merch: https://www.ibxrunning.com/store
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/ibxrunning/

00:00 - Intro
00:25 - Warm Up
03:25 - Workout!
13:25 - Cool Down
